\sin\theta=\frac{2t}{1+t^2}\qquad\cos\theta=\frac{1-t^2}{1+t^2}.
\left(\frac{2t}{1+t^2}\right)^2-\left(\frac{1-t^2}{1+t^2}\right)^2\overset{?}{=}1-2\left(\frac{1-t^2}{1+t^2}\right)^2.
(2t)^2-(1-t^2)^2\overset{?}{=}(1+t^2)^2-2(1-t^2)^2.
